{"tid":1904074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"諗極到諗唔明爭奪功能組別有咩問題","createTime":"2020-02-29T11:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T01:18:26.000Z","uid":34811,"like":55,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"08a3ec3c35dc825562456a82edde3969b5b7deb8","tid":1904074,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:34:09.000Z","msg":"我見好多人講到參加功能組別就代表認同功能組表呢個制度，當手足係condom<br />\n<br />\n其實我睇唔明點解參加功能組別就代表支持功能組別，反對真普通選<br />\n<br />\n區議會立法會要簽確認書，又有DQ咁，參選同投票係咪又代表支持DQ支持有確認書制度？(熱狗會叫人投白票，但係又走去選)<br />\n<br />\n遊行集會搞手申請不反係咪又代表認同公安條例？<br />\n<br />\n係人都知好難贏，贏到都未必有用，但係咪咁就唔做？依家唔係dead body果陣話乜柒要守住關鏈缺席，依家冇人出嚟選就變咗奶共派自動當選<br />\n<br />\n抗爭要做，文宣要做，黃色經濟圈要做，國際戰線要做，議會戰線一樣要做，唔會做咗一樣第二樣就冇人理<br />\n<br />\n最後泛民咪以為我會同你含撚投票，你試下再搵白頭廢老去選超區，跟住搞埋啲on9嘢話幾多月生日就去配票俾白頭佬，睬你到on9<br />\n<br />\n支持爭奪功能組別唔代表會同你含，我勸梁耀忠黃碧雲楊岳橋，同埋唔知派別嘅鄭松泰就唔好出嚟選，留返個位俾本土派"},{"pid":"0da8f21d8ddec721aad6127b831fe7baece2b1bb","tid":1904074,"uid":34811,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"樓主泛民打手，好驚輸？<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"9f269467b9388a8992e88073fc03877568278b36","tid":1904074,"uid":51621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得你講得岩"},{"pid":"0ea86aea28c4c4aa6fc193d6b53e08b57b583a0a","tid":1904074,"uid":59192,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:39:02.000Z","msg":"總之投泛民都唔投保皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問你中共驚未"},{"pid":"110ffa0c389ba2194605c27aad0bafcd255f36c5","tid":1904074,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0da8f21d8ddec721aad6127b831fe7baece2b1bb","tid":1904074,"uid":34811,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"樓主泛民打手，好驚輸？<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343397247c10df21134c484c052c203b3b748902","tid":1904074,"uid":129011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:11:48.000Z","msg":"呢啲post冇人推嘅?"},{"pid":"a44d47483152d84ee9c3354326d46be3d2ecf5f2","tid":1904074,"uid":22888,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"因為d人要分化 先話有問題"},{"pid":"c8cd716eb69ddc841d06e6518fac6130ab5446c4","tid":1904074,"uid":56017,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:14:59.000Z","msg":"好老實講，我地一直都係處於分裂唔團結唔盡力既狀態<br />\n所以立法會議席先會有咁大差別<br />\n未盡過力，點會知結果<br />\n咩方法都試下，當然勇武繼續做"},{"pid":"1b496f9b741363a1f61d470130d231727a6791df","tid":1904074,"uid":290393,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0da8f21d8ddec721aad6127b831fe7baece2b1bb","tid":1904074,"uid":34811,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"樓主泛民打手，好驚輸？<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:15:23.000Z","msg":"你同自己講野？未記得換acc?"},{"pid":"649e0d5c8cb7909e52d52f7a95280a9d6031ac35","tid":1904074,"uid":237300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔明有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同叫人投白票一樣"},{"pid":"6945c0ca983e32b995fa8a2560348e9a085cec78","tid":1904074,"uid":80890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b496f9b741363a1f61d470130d231727a6791df","tid":1904074,"uid":290393,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0da8f21d8ddec721aad6127b831fe7baece2b1bb","tid":1904074,"uid":34811,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"樓主泛民打手，好驚輸？<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:15:23.000Z","msg":"你同自己講野？未記得換acc?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4f14fb4fe7a6dd950671c92a8c2e880e54552f","tid":1904074,"uid":22888,"like":0,"disl